<p>Faculty members in the BIAC are leaders in imaging methodology development,&nbsp;analysis techniques, as well as in their application in cognitive and clinical neurosciences. In addition, BIAC offers imaging services to other faculty members on campus and at the University of North Carolina in Chapel Hill.&nbsp;</p>

